32:56.933 --> 33:00.312
<i>was not something Mr Simon
should include on his resume.</i>

33:00.437 --> 33:01.480
Tell me something I don't know.

33:02.481 --> 33:03.690
So, you're saying you like homos?

33:04.232 --> 33:05.275
Yeah, right.

33:06.610 --> 33:08.320
Take it easy, Andy.

33:19.498 --> 33:23.084
ANDY: <i>Another thing you never do
