33:23.168 --> 33:25.545
<i>I decided to investigate
the allegation myself.</i>

33:25.670 --> 33:27.339
- Hey, Dire?
-Yeah?

33:27.464 --> 33:30.050
You knew Mr Simon was a homo, right?

33:30.133 --> 33:31.510
Where you been, Nichol?

33:33.512 --> 33:34.513
Jimmy, Jimmy!

33:35.472 --> 33:37.515
I hear Simon's a homo?

33:37.516 --> 33:39.059
Nichol, seriously?

33:39.142 --> 33:40.977
What's it like to go around
with your head up your butt?

33:43.146 --> 33:44.522
Good afternoon, everyone!

33:44.523 --> 33:46.525
Good afternoon, Mr Simon.

33:46.566 --> 33:47.651
I have an announcement to make.

33:48.485 --> 33:50.695
The car I won in the newspaper contest
has arrived,

33:50.779 --> 33:54.199
